reviewText:
Edenquest: Anna Nicole Smith is one hour and released on video on January 1, 2002. This Edenquest takes place on the Bahamas islands. In the opening scene we see a lot of beautiful topless models and then Anna Nicole Smith jumps in as our host. She is scene nude for about ten seconds and that is being liberal in the early part of the show. Then we are introduced to the six models one at a time and stuff that they did in the Bahamas. The models are:

Chrisy Adkins
Lisa Falcone
Sung Hi Lee
Galle Comparat
Elina Alvarez
Lisa Boyle

At the conclusion of the video the head photographer gives his opinion about each model. We end the video with three of the models having a pillow fight. I sorry, but my definition of nude is no cloths at all. I can only give Edenquest: Anna Nicole Smith a D+.
